    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Black- or green-glass bottles of quart and pint sizes, used primarily for beers, porter, cider, spring water, and other popular potables.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
